♪Holding the same fervent hopes♪

170
00:13:23,540 --> 00:13:25,580
♪For nameless souls♪

171
00:13:25,820 --> 00:13:27,740
♪With light in my heart,
I fear no darkness♪

172
00:13:28,020 --> 00:13:30,220
♪Restoring the purity
of mountains and rivers to the world♪

173
